<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Vestemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, als ir von Kraften,
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> suns, bey uns wart, wiszet ir wol, wie
                        ir darumb von uns schiedt. Nu schreibt er uns, wie uns
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burgg<ex>ra</ex>f</expan> Fridrich <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> seinen
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab. <expan>Lass<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                        ew wissen, daz wir seinen <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darauf
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dann, wie ir von des
                            <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> suns <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> uns geschieden
                        seit. Wil er das noch also vollenden <expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        und <app><note><q type="date"><expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>nehst<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sant Michels tag</q>29.09.1412</note></app>, so sol es dabey
                                <expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wie wol er das bisher
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan> hat, und sol auch
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czeit sicher sein <add>vor</add>
                        uns und den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> v <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>assumpt<ex>i</ex>o<ex>nis</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
